title: Selena Gomez's makeup-free selfie on Instagram gets over 8 million likes
text:
Selena Gomez recently posted a selfie that was quite the opposite of her usual glamorous image.

On Instagram, she posted a photo captioned "Me, all the time." In it, she appears to be wearing no makeup -- which isn't the norm for the entertainer.

Since posting, Gomez's makeup-free selfie has gained lots of traction, and has over 8 million likes.

In addition to likes, many commented on the picture.

Stephane Cardinale/Corbis via Getty Images, FILE

One person presumed that she was thinking about Justin Bieber's recent wedding to Hailey Baldwin. While another person wrote, "What’s going on with u Sel? Please be healthy, take care of urself and get well, we love u and wait for ur work."

The 27-year-old's Instagram feed shows that she appeared to go makeup-free in September while posing with her friend Anna Collins.
description: Selena Gomez posted a makeup-free selfie and fans react.
